metadata.name: Angel Rising
metadata.description:
ANGEL RISING is about having the courage to go beyond your 
fears, transcending to new worlds and experiences to fulfill your destiny.       

This artwork aims to inspire taking action towards your goals and living a full earthly experience. 

Every step is progress and one day you may just leap, learn to fly and reach your dreams.

Are we humans or could we be angels rising?

“What if I fall, oh but my darling what if you fly?” - J.M. Barrie


Freediver: Angela Tseng

Photographed in an underwater cave in Maui, Hawaii on Dec 5th, 2022.
